data.name: grd_satsang_centre_id.LookupColumns
data.value:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-16"?> <Root LookupSqlQuery="SELECT s.satsang_centre_id, centre_cd = COALESCE(scd.centre_cd, s.satsang_centre_cd), centre_nm = COALESCE(scd.centre_nm, s.satsang_centre_nm) FROM satsang_centres_details scd 
 JOIN CDB..satsang_centres s ON s.satsang_centre_id = scd.satsang_centre_id
WHERE scd.is_main_centre = 'Yes' AND ?"> <LookupColumn caption="Satsang Centre Id" sqlName="satsang_centre_id" aliasName="satsang_centre_id" percentageWidth="25" toolTipText="Satsang Centre Id" isDisplayMemberColumn="False" isValueMemberColumn="True" isCodeMemberColumn="False" tablePrefix="s" /> <LookupColumn caption="Centre Code" sqlName="COALESCE(scd.centre_cd, s.satsang_centre_cd)" aliasName="centre_cd" percentageWidth="25" toolTipText="Centre Code" isDisplayMemberColumn="False" isValueMemberColumn="False" isCodeMemberColumn="True" tablePrefix="" /> <LookupColumn caption="Centre Name" sqlName="COALESCE(scd.centre_nm, s.satsang_centre_nm)" aliasName="centre_nm" percentageWidth="50" toolTipText="Centre Name" isDisplayMemberColumn="True" isValueMemberColumn="False" isCodeMemberColumn="False" tablePrefix="" /> </Root>
